[h1]Case Sensitivity[/h1]

SQL is case [b]insensitive[/b]. 
The following statements are equivalent and will produce the same result: [code format="sql"][b]select [/b]City from customers;
[b]SELECT [/b]City FROM customers;
[b]sElEct [/b]City From customers;[/code]
[note]It is common practice to write all SQL commands in [b]upper-case[/b].[/note]
